{"id": "1395299113683259472", "channel_id": "1395299113683259472", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "🕛️**集合时间：**晚上12点\n🗺️**集合地点：**离你最近的墓园，找到一口石质棺椁，躺进去并压低呼吸\n👜**必带物品：**\n腐味试剂：它能掩盖你的活人气息\n羽绒服：葬骸城终年被寒雾包裹，温度极低\n🏛️**著名景点：**\n◆鬼王的大锅：杜勒赛因曾用此锅烹饪令人惊叹的美味，想来锅里暖和下吗？\n◆葬骸城古街：眼球蜜饯、尸妆定制、小肠风铃……应有尽有。\n◆破屋艺术展：注入天才画师全部生命与疯狂的完美作品！患心脏疾病者请谨慎入场。\n……更多景点等待您亲自发现……\n\n🤵🏻葬骸城民风淳朴、热情好客，定能给您带来宾至如归的体验~\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n🕛 **MEET-UP TIME: **Midnight sharp.\n🗺 **MEET-UP SPOT: **Your nearest graveyard. Find a stone coffin, hop in, and try not to breathe too loud.\n👜** PACKING LIST:**\nRot Potion: Masks that pesky \"living\" smell.\nPuffer Jacket: Necrovia’s eternal mist is bone-chilling.\n🏛 **MUST-SEE ATTRACTIONS:**\n◆The Ghoul King’s Cauldron: \nHis Majesty Doresain once whipped up unholy delicacies here. Fancy a warm dip?\n◆Necrovia Old Street: \nEyeball candy, corpse couture, intestine wind chimes… Shop 'til you drop!\n◆Abandoned Gallery: \nWhere a certain mad painter poured his soul into every stroke—literally. Heart conditions? Skip this one.\n\n…More delightful surprises await...\n\n🤵🏻Our locals are ***dying*** to meet you! Expect warm welcomes, great service, and a sense of belonging so deep, you ***might stay forever***~", "timestamp": "2025-07-17T07:00:32.106000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 14}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1395299114203222076", "filename": "3-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1532108, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1395299113683259472/1395299114203222076/3-.jpg?ex=69ccc290&is=69cb7110&hm=02438b2da6147ac7712a39eedc052048a6744930842b8794b69c6d7e0d95b084&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1395299113683259472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3 杜勒赛因情报：葬骸